{"sequence":19,"timestamp":"2026-04-06T15:06:55.314381111Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-7bdc647a","body":"In derive_resume_state() (engine.rs ~line 6355), add a handler for JournalEventType::StageSkipped that advances next_stage_index past the skipped stage, mirroring the StageCompleted handler: `next_stage_index = stage_index_for(stage_plan, skipped_stage_id)? + 1`. Without this, a crash during FinalReview after ApplyFixes was skipped will cause resume to re-run ApplyFixes instead of resuming at FinalReview.","dedup_key":"1d2b75d45f482d0f47ffda55f9917613f48da34cd7f0c7b034af113febbc19ac","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"claude","model_id":"claude-opus-4-6","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260406142347","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":20,"timestamp":"2026-04-06T15:06:55.324124537Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-1-34cfb1c3","body":"Handle `JournalEventType::StageSkipped` during resume reconstruction. `src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:4591-4638` now journals a `stage_skipped` event for `apply_fixes`, but `src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:6355-6421` never advances `next_stage_index` when that event is present. If the run fails after the skip is committed but before `final_review` starts, for example because `write_run_snapshot` or checkpointing fails in `src/contexts/workflow_composition/engine.rs:4688-4752`, `run resume` will incorrectly restart at `apply_fixes` instead of `final_review`. That produces inconsistent durable history (`stage_skipped` followed by a later execution of the same stage/cycle) and reintroduces the backend call this change is meant to avoid. Add `StageSkipped` handling in `derive_resume_state()` and a regression test for resume after a post-skip failure.","dedup_key":"1246e827fe6a891f3183dddb1bcb05a844e48276f257532fa482ee4d0ea9ce4d","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260406142347","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
